                  </hi>. I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted</hi> 16<hi rend="italic">th of June</hi>, 1845, <hi rend="italic">and confined six days</hi>)—the pri<lb></lb>soner is the person.</p>
